\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">分</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">每封一罐</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">从头道卷边滚轮开始卷封至二道滚轮结束</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">卷封的时间为</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">13/30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">秒</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">,<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">头道滚轮的卷封工艺角为29.5°。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">求安装若将头道行星齿轮偏心轴孔的中心放在最里位置</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">则三道行星齿轮偏心轴孔的中心应由最里位置逆其自转方向放过多少个齿</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">中心齿轮与行星轮的齿数比为</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">且行星齿轮齿数为</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">28)?</span></span></p>','','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/edit/attached/20110906/20110906162659_69675.bmp\" />');
