;color:#000000;\">◎ </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">操纵机构可分为</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">单独操纵机构</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">集中操纵机构</span></span></nobr></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"text-align:justify;\"><nobr><span style=\"font-family:黑体;mso-ascii-font-family:黑体;mso-fareast-font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;font-size:24pt;color:#003366;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">◎</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> 单独操纵机构</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">可分为</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">摆动式</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">移动式</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">两大类</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;ms