ize:20pt;color:#003366;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">○</span></span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;mso-ascii-font-family:黑体;mso-fareast-font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;font-size:24pt;color:#003366;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">摆杆端部滑块的运动轨迹是圆弧，滑块在滑移齿轮的环形槽内相对滑移齿轮的轴线有偏移</span></span></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"text-align:justify;\"><nobr><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;mso-ascii-font-family:黑体;mso-fareast-font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;font-size:20pt;color:#003366;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">○</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> 操作力随着偏移量的增加而增大</span></span></nobr></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"text-align:justify;\"><nobr><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;mso-ascii-font-family:黑体;mso-fareast-font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;font-size:20pt;color:#003366;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">○</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> 机构设计时，应力求减少该偏移量，</span></span></nobr></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:20pt;color:#003366;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">○</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> 可将摆杆轴线配置在滑移齿轮行程的中点垂直面内，同时正确选择摆杆的旋转半径，使滑块相对于滑移齿轮轴线的上下偏移量相等 </span></span></div>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-spacing:\" 100=\"\" 50=\"\" 0\"\"=\"\"></div>\n</div>\n<nobr> </nobr><p></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-spacing:\" 100=\"\" 50=\"\" 0\"\"=\"\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme>',0,NULL,'999999',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (433,165,'第二节  定位互锁机构',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','','2011-08-02 21:07:31','<p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b> </b><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#e56600;\"><b>定位装置设计要求</b></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">◎ 应有足够的定位精度和刚度，且定位精度能够长期保持</span></span></p>\n<p>◎ 定位动作迅速、平稳、可靠</p>\n<p>◎ 定位元件磨损后易于调整和更换</p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n<p></p>\n<hr />\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><p><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">定位装置的类型</span></b></p>\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">◎ 弹性定位装置</span></span></p>\n<p>◎ 刚性定位装置</p>\n<p>◎ 弹性定位装置的设计计算</p>\n<p>◎ 旋转运动互锁装置</p>\n<p>◎ 直线运动互锁装置</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;color:#000000;\"><hr />\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">互锁机构</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><b><span style=\"color:#000000;\">◎ </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">直线运动互锁装置</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#e56600;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><embed src=\"http://bzjx.nit.net.cn/uploads/movie/11-2-1.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"550\" height=\"400\" quality=\"high\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#e56600;\"></p>\n<hr />\n</p:colorscheme><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><b><span style=\"color:#000000;\">◎ </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">直线、旋转运动复合互锁装置</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#e56600;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><img src=\"/edit/attached/20110804/20110804100529_97123.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"230\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme></div>\n</p:colorscheme></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><p style=\"font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"></p:colorscheme></span></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"></p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"></p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"></p:colorscheme></span></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div><nobr> </nobr></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme><p></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme></div>\n</p:colorscheme></div>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme></div>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme><p></p>\n</span></span><p style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"></p>\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"> </span><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"font-weight:bold;text-align:left;white-space:nowrap;\"></div>\n<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"> </span><p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-spacing:\" 100=\"\" 50=\"\" 0\"\"=\"\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme>',0,NULL,'999999',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (434,165,'第三节 包装机械润滑系统设计',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','','2011-08-02 21:11:05','<div>◎ 正确润滑，可减小相对运动零部件工作表面的摩擦和磨损，降低系统温升，减少能量损耗，提高零部件使用寿命，保持机械工作精度，提高机器工作效率</div>\n<div>◎ 包装机常用润滑剂有润滑油和润滑脂</div>\n<div>◎ 润滑方式有稀油润滑和干油润滑</div>\n<div><hr />\n<div><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">润滑方式的选择</span></b></div>\n<div><b>◎ 稀油润滑方式</b></div>\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 完成润滑任务，同时带走摩擦面间产生的热量；</div>\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 保证滑动平面之间的摩擦为液体摩擦，如：液体摩擦轴承、止推滑动轴承及高速移动的滑动平面之间等；</div>\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 齿轮传动箱及箱内密封轴承的润滑；</div>\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 通过油杯方式对转动和滑动副进行的润滑。</div>\n<div><b>◎ 干油润滑方式</b></div>\n<div>降低接触零部件的摩擦阻力、减少磨损</div>\n<div>润滑油（脂）的供给方法</div>\n<div><b>◎ 稀油润滑的供油方式</b></div>\n<div><div><div><hr />\n</div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">稀油集中润滑系统设计</span></b></span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">◎ 设计步骤如下：</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 全面了解包装机的润滑要求；</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 掌握润滑系统设计和计算所需要的有关数据；</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 确定合理的润滑方案；</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 根据确定的方案，计算出各机构运动副的摩擦损失率，换算出润滑油的总耗量；</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 选定并核算润滑系统各项设备及元件型号、规格及数量</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 确定管路尺寸，绘制管路系统图和布置图，验算管路的压力损失。</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#e56600;\"><b>选择润滑系统形式的基本原则</b></span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">○如润滑油的消耗量大于400L／min，或者虽小于400L／min，但属重要的机械系统，应设计成自动循环润滑系统；</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;○ 同一机组中，相似机械应尽量采用同一种润滑油，摩擦副类似且距离较近的机械（相距不大于30～40m）应采用同一个润滑站；</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;○ 工作制度不同的机械设备，摩擦副给油方式不同的的设备，摩擦副构造不同的设备，不能统一到同一个集中润滑系统中；</span></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;○ 油号有特殊要求和容易污染的摩擦部件应单独设置润滑油站。</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n</div>',0,NULL,'999999',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (435,166,'第一节  概述',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','','2011-08-02 21:14:25','<p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b> </b><p><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">一、</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">包装生产线定义</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">包装自动生产线</span></span><span style=\"color:#e56600;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">：按照产品的包装工艺过程，利用分流、合流、</span></span><span style=\"color:#e56600;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">储存、传送装置把包装机以及辅助设备连接起来，而形成的有独</span></span><span style=\"color:#e56600;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">立控制装置的包装生产系统。在包装生产线上，被包装物上线后</span></span><span style=\"color:#e56600;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">，以一定的生产节拍，按照设定的包装工艺顺序，经过各个包装</span></span><span style=\"color:#e56600;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">工位，完成预定的包装作业后再下线。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">包装生产线自动化程度</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">取决于人参与生产的程度</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">。</span></span></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">自动包装生产线</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">：被包装物自动地经过各个包装工位完成预定包</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">装，工人不直接参与工艺操作，只是全面观察、分析生产系统的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">运转情况，定期地上、下料，对包装质量进行抽样检查，及时排</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">除设备故障，调整、维修和保养设备，保证自动包装生产线的连</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">续运转。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b style=\"color:#000000;\"> </b></p:colorscheme></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">二、自动包装生产线优点</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#e56600;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></span></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">有利于应用先进的科学技术和现代企业管理技术，简化生产布局，减少生产工人数量、中间仓库和被包装物贮备量，缩短生产周期，提高包装产品质量，提高劳动生产率，降低生产成本，改善劳动条件，促进企业生产实现现代化。</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b> </b><p><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">三</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">、自动包装生产线</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">缺</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">点</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">投入成本高，占地面积大，生产组织管理的水平要求高</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"></p>\n<hr />\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">四</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">、</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">组成</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\"> </span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:left;\">五、包装生产线分类</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> <div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">按</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">包装生产工艺路线</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">的不同：直线型、台阶型、回转型和组合型</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">按自动包装生产线的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">组合方式</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">不同：串联型、并联型和串并联混</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">合型</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">按自动包装生产线的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">组合方式</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">不同：串联型、并联型和串并联混</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">合型</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">按包装生产线</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">布置方式</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">的不同：直线型、曲线型、环形和树枝型</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">按</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">包装产品或成品的性状</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">不同：流体或半流体包装线、粉粒状物</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">品包装线、颗粒状物品包装线、块状物品包装线</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">按产品在自动线上的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">移动特征</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">：间歇运动型、连续运动型和间歇</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">与连续并存型</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">按包装机间</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">连接特征</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">的不同：</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">刚性型、柔性型和半柔性型</span></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<div style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:133%;color:red;\"><span style=\"mso-special-format:bullet;position:absolute;left:-3.48%;font-family:Wingdings;\">&#216;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">刚性生产线。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">同一生产线、同一节拍工作。一台故障，全线停</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">止 </span></span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:133%;color:red;\"><span style=\"position:absolute;left:-3.48%;font-family:Wingdings;font-size:12px;\">&#216;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">挠性生产线。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">前道包装工序完成后，经中间贮存装置贮存，送</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">至下一包装工序。某台故障，不会立刻影响全线生产</span></span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><div><span style=\"font-size:133%;color:red;\"><span style=\"position:absolute;left:-3.48%;font-family:Wingdings;font-size:12px;\">&#216;</span></span><p style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;color:red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">半挠性生产线。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">生产线由若干区段组成，每区段以刚性联接，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">各区段间为挠性联接。如灌装生产线，其中灌装机与压盖机常</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">以刚性联接组成机组</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:16px;line-height:48px;color:#e56600;\">设计自动包装线关键因素：</span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">1）前序包装机的生产能力高于后序包装</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">机生产能力10~15%</span></b></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\">\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><div><b><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">2）缓冲存储区域</span></b></div>\n<div class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-spacing:\" 100=\"\" 500\";mso-text-indent-alt:168;\"=\"\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme></div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme><p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme><p></p>',0,NULL,'999999',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (436,166,'第二节  包装生产线设计',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','','2011-08-02 21:18:22','<p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b> </b><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<p><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">一、总体设计</span></b></p>\n<p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> <p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">总体设计整个设计最重要的环节，总体设计正确、合理与否，对</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">生产线的生产效率、运行可靠性、设备复杂程度、成本造价、生</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">产节拍等起决定性的作用，决定整条生产线项目的成功与否</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b style=\"color:#000000;\"> </b></p:colorscheme></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">注意事项</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\">\n\n<div class=\"O4\" style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">对包装物和包装材料形状、特性进行充分研究</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">考虑包装物品是否能以稳定正常的状态进入下道包</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">装工序</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">对自动包装线设置合适的中间缓冲储存区</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">使内、外包装机的生产能力匹配。</span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">总体设计的主要内容</span></b><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<div style=\"color:#000000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:red;\">1. 包装工艺路线的设计</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">保证包装质量基础上，力求高效率、低成本、结构简单、便于自</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">动控制</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#000000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:red;\">2．自动包装线布置形式的选择</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:#0000cc;\"> </span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">考虑被包装物特点、生产纲领、生产条件等因素，分析不同类型</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">生产线优缺点，确定生产线布置形式。</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#000000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:red;\">3. 生产节拍、输送速度的确定</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">根据生产纲领、自动线布置形式、工位最长工艺时间、工件传送</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">平稳性要求，确定间歇型自动线的生产节拍，或确定连续型自动</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">线的输送速度</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#000000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:red;\">4. 自动控制系统的确定</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"> </span><p style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">采用PLC控制还是采用计算机控制；是采用时序控制、行程控制还</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">是混合控制；是采用集中控制还是分散控制；是采用机械控制、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">流体控制还是采用电器控制</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">二、工艺路线设计</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O1\">\n\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">合理选择包装材料和包装容器</span></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">满足工序的集中与分散</span></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">选择工艺路线的形式</span></div>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;\"> </span><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:#000000;\">平衡工序的节拍</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#e56600;\"></p>\n<hr />\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><p style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#e56600;\">满足工序的集中与分散</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></span></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 采用</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">工序集中</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，可减少中间输送、储存、转向等环节，使机构得</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">以简化，缩减生产线的占地面积。工序过分集中，会对包装工艺</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">增加更多的限制，降低生产线的通用性，增加机构的复杂程度。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">采用集中工序时，应保证调整、维修方便，运行可靠，有一定通</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">用性。</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">采用</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">工序分散</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，可提高生产率，平衡工序的生产节拍，减小</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">机构的复杂程度，提高工作可靠性，便于设备调整和维修等。例</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">如：回转式自动灌装机头数愈多，生产率愈高</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"></p>\n<hr />\n<p></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">三、设备选型</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">遵循</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">生产适用、技术先进、经济合理</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">原则</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">1</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">设备的技术先进性</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">2. 设备的可靠性</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">3. 设备的经济性</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">4. 设备的消耗性</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">5. 设备的操作性、安全性</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div style=\"color:#e56600;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">6. 设备的成套性</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">7. 设备的灵活性</span></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8. 设备的维护性 &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<hr />\n<p>\n&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#e56600;font-family:宋体;\"><b>四、设备布局</b></span></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">简单、实用、经济的原则布置设备</span></p:colorscheme></p>\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><b>1.平面布置</b></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">应力求生产线短、布局紧凑、占地面积小齐美观以及调整、操作、维修方便&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><b>2.立面布置</b></span></p>\n<p>综合考虑包装工序特点、厂房大小及高度、人员行走方便、卫生安全条件的诸多因素，可将自动包装生产线进行立面布置，力求降低成本、因地制宜、灵活安排</p>\n<p><hr />\n</p>\n</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\"><embed src=\"http://bzjx.nit.net.cn/uploads/movie/12-2-1.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"550\" height=\"400\" quality=\"high\" /></span></p>\n<p></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\"><embed src=\"http://bzjx.nit.net.cn/uploads/movie/12-2-2.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"550\" height=\"400\" quality=\"high\" /></span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O1\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\"><br />\n</span></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;font-size:12px;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme><p></p>\n</span><p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div class=\"O\" style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div></div>\n</div>\n<p>\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-spacing:\" 100=\"\" 50=\"\" 0\"\"=\"\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme>',0,NULL,'999999',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (437,166,'第三节 辅助装置',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','','2011-08-02 21:22:35','<p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b> </b><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#e56600;\"><b>一、分流装置</b><br />\n<p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> <div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<div><span style=\"color:#000000;\">1）送料装置工作能力大；</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div><span style=\"color:#000000;\">2）生产能力大的装置向生产能力小的装置送料；</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div><span style=\"color:#000000;\">3）自动分拣机；</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><div><span style=\"color:#000000;\">4）产品以单列流过输送带，按一定数量分别包装。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></div>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-spacing:&quot;100 50 0&quot;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme>',0,NULL,'999999',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (438,166,'第四节  典型包装生产线示例',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','','2011-08-02 21:23:24','<p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b> </b><p><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">PVC粉料全自动称重包装码垛生产线</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">用于PVC粉料的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">自动称重、包装、输送检测及码垛</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，主要</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">由</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">上料单元、称重单元、包装单元、输送检测单元、码</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">垛单元</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">以及辅助的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">除尘单元、真空与气动单元</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">等组成</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><embed src=\"http://bzjx.nit.net.cn/uploads/movie/12-4-1.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"550\" height=\"400\" quality=\"high\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><hr />\n<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b style=\"color:#000000;\"> </b></p:colorscheme></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">自动包装生产线工作过程</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">上料机构将待包装的粉粒状物料送至电子定量秤，经电</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">子称的分料器进入全自动称重、包装系统，实现物料</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">的全自动称重、包装，装满物料的料袋经过整形、缝</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">口、热封工序后，送入金属检测机和电子复检秤，含</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">有金属及重量不合格的料袋被自动拣选机剔除，合格</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">的料袋继续输送，喷墨打码后，送入码垛单元，完成</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">最后的整形、编组、码垛工序，垛盘由叉车下线入库</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b style=\"color:#000000;\"> </b></p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">称重原理</span></b></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></p>\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">电子定量秤对物料进行全自动称重，为自动包装机提供定量的物料，称重工作过程如下：前一次称重、卸料完毕后，</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">放料气缸驱动称重箱翻门关闭，四连杆并联给料气缸驱动落料闸门全打开，进行粗给料；粗给料结束后，落料闸门关</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">闭至细流口，进行精给料，同时，悬臂式电阻应变称重传感器测量物料的重量；当物料重量达到包装要求时，落料闸</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">门全关闭，称重箱翻门打开，向空包装袋充填，完成一次自动称重过程。</span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><hr />\n<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b style=\"color:#000000;\"> </b></p:colorscheme></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">自动拣选机原理</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\"> </span></b></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#e56600;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></span></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<div><span style=\"color:#000000;\">用于不合格料袋的剔除及合格料袋的输送</span></div>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">拣选机由拣选机构和输送机构组成，分别由减速电机驱动。输送</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">机构的减速电机通过链条传动带动链轮输送辊转动，完成料袋的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">输送，其输送速度与输送线速度相匹配。拣选机构通过气缸活塞</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">杆推动翻转架升起，将料袋抬升离开输送机的输送辊，同时拣选</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">电机启动，驱动皮带轮转动，将料袋从输送线上剔除，剔除的料</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">袋由下线托盘滑下。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">拣选机的工作状态是由金属检测机与电子复检秤输出的检测信号</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">控制，当物料的金属检测及重量检测结果合格时，拣选机构不工</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">作，当对物料的金属检测或重量检测不合格时，控制系统发出指</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">令，拣选机的输送机停止运转，拣选机构动作，将料袋从输送线</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">上剔除 </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><hr />\n</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><embed src=\"http://bzjx.nit.net.cn/uploads/movie/12-4-2.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"550\" height=\"400\" quality=\"high\" /></p>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;\">\n</div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>',0,NULL,'999999',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (439,166,'第五节  包装生产线生产效率',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','','2011-08-02 21:25:45','<p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><b> </b><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n\n<p><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">一、包装自动生产线的生产率</span></b></p>\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;\">二、影响生产线生产率的因素</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#e56600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">刚性包装生产线，随着包装机台数的增加，生产率相</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">应提高，但不是简单的正比关系。当台数增加到一定</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">数量后，再增加包装机台数，生产率反而下降。这主</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">要是因为循环外时间损失成为影响生产率的主要因素</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span></span></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">挠性包装生产线，随着包装机台数的增加，生产率初</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">始提高得很快，随后变得缓慢，直至稳定。在循环外</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">时间损失相同的条件下，挠性包装生产线的生产率总</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">高于刚性生平线。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">半挠性生产线，其分段数对生产率也有影响，包装生</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">产线分段时应有利于减小循环外时间损失，提高生产</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">率。</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<hr />\n<p></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><p style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">三</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">、</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\">提高生产线生产率的途径</span><span style=\"color:#e56600;\"> </span></b></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#e56600;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"> </p:colorscheme></span></p>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">1.减小包装机的 &nbsp; T<span style=\"font-size:9px;\">k、Tf、</span>∑Tn</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">2.增加包装机台数可提高包装工艺速度，减小基本工艺时间</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">3.采用先进设备，提高设备本身的可靠性</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">4.采用连续型包装机，尽可能减少或消除辅助操作时间</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">5.采用若干台包装机并联完成</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">6.加强设备检修和维护保养</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">7.采用必要的电器设备控制系统并设置必要的自动检测系统，减少故障造成的停机损失</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\" style=\"text-align:left;\">8.提高生产和组织者的操作水平和管理水平</div>\n<div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\"><div><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"line-height:48px;font-family:宋体;font-size:x-large;\"><p:colorscheme colors=\"#ffffff,#000000,#b2b2b2,#000000,#b2b2b2,#808080,#969696,#4d4d4d\"><div v:shape=\"_x0000_s1026\" class=\"O\">\n<div style=\"font-weight:800;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme></span></div>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#000000;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:left;\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#e56600;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-spacing:\" 100=\"\" 50=\"\" 0\"\"=\"\"></div>\n</div>\n</p:colorscheme>',0,NULL,'999999',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
